contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:54.625 --> 00:55.875
<i>I was always wondering...</i>

00:56.375 --> 00:58.750
<i>what my future would be like.</i>

01:02.500 --> 01:03.167
Good morning, Truly.

01:03.292 --> 01:03.625
Morning.

01:03.750 --> 01:05.458
<i>Graduate from my dream school,</i>

01:05.583 --> 01:06.667
<i>fully develop my potential,</i>

01:06.792 --> 01:07.750
<i>realize my dreams.</i>

01:07.875 --> 01:10.208
Bravo!

01:11.583 --> 01:12.875
The lucrative deal in Shenzhen

01:13.583 --> 01:15.292
is finally signed to us.

01:15.750 --> 01:16.667
Listen,

01:17.375 --> 01:18.708
you should learn more from Truly.

01:18.833 --> 01:20.375
Do everything you can for the company.

01:20.500 --> 01:22.458
Fight for more good deals!

01:22.583 --> 01:23.333
Cheers!

01:23.458 --> 01:25.042
Thank you boss.

01:25.167 --> 01:25.792
Thank you.

01:25.917 --> 01:26.500
WOW!

01:26.625 --> 01:28.208
What is this, Truly?

01:28.333 --> 01:29.667
So shiny!

01:30.208 --> 01:31.792
Congratulations!

01:32.500 --> 01:34.917
Double good news!

01:35.500 --> 01:37.875
<i>And have a perfect relationship.</i>

01:38.875 --> 01:41.167
<i>My life will shine...</i>

01:41.292 --> 01:42.583
<i>like a diamond.</i>

01:54.833 --> 01:56.292
Hsin, go tell her.

01:57.625 --> 01:59.083
We've worked over time for so many days...

01:59.208 --> 02:00.167
Truly.

02:00.792 --> 02:02.458
Can we go now?

02:02.792 --> 02:04.750
Sure, bye bye!

02:04.875 --> 02:05.667
Bye bye.

02:05.792 --> 02:06.792
See you tomorrow. -Bye bye.

02:06.917 --> 02:07.750
Thank you, Truly!

02:07.875 --> 02:08.625
Hurray!

02:08.750 --> 02:09.667
Shall we got for spicy hot pot?

02:09.792 --> 02:10.250
Sure.

02:10.375 --> 02:12.125
Which restaurant? <i>I'll</i> make a reservation.

02:12.250 --> 02:12.833
Hello?

02:12.958 --> 02:14.292
What time do you think it is?

02:14.625 --> 02:16.208
Why are you still in the office?

02:16.333 --> 02:17.667
I've been waiting for 5 minutes.

02:17.792 --> 02:18.500
Sorry.

02:18.625 --> 02:19.667
<i>I'll</i> go to the restaurant now.

02:19.792 --> 02:21.458
If you're not here in 5 minutes, <i>I'll</i> leave.

02:21.583 --> 02:22.708
That's not enough time!

02:22.833 --> 02:25.083
<i>It'll</i> take me half an hour to get there.

02:25.208 --> 02:26.917
Hello?

02:27.792 --> 02:28.833
Shit.

02:30.625 --> 02:32.292
Conference call with Edinburgh at midnight.

02:32.417 --> 02:34.667
Your team will stay to prepare for it.

02:34.792 --> 02:35.917
Butlhaveu.

02:47.792 --> 02:49.417
<i>I'll do it</i> now.

02:52.958 --> 02:54.458
Look at Truly.

02:54.792 --> 02:55.708
What a role model!

02:58.500 --> 02:59.542
Yes, sir.

03:01.708 --> 03:03.167
Everyone.

03:03.667 --> 03:06.042
Let's stay a little longer to work on it.

03:06.167 --> 03:07.208
Go! Go! Go!

03:07.333 --> 03:09.458
Earlier done, earlier home.

03:13.542 --> 03:15.583
<i>No one ever told me,</i>

03:15.708 --> 03:17.333
<i>the truth is...when you grow up,</i>

03:17.458 --> 03:20.250
<i>it's likely you'll have a not-so-good job,</i>

03:20.375 --> 03:22.750
<i>be in a not-so-good relationship,</i>

03:23.208 --> 03:26.833
<i>and live a not-so-good life.</i>

03:27.583 --> 03:29.042
...dunno what he wants to eat.

03:29.167 --> 03:31.500
It seems like Hsin is on a diet...

03:32.375 --> 03:35.958
Go! Go !Go! Early done, early home.

03:36.750 --> 03:38.375
She's the one who told us to stay.

03:38.500 --> 03:40.167
I won't get her bonus anyway.

03:40.292 --> 03:42.542
The manager told us to learn from Truly.

03:42.667 --> 03:44.500
Fuck! Who wants to learn from her?

03:44.625 --> 03:47.167
Working overtime for little salary.

03:47.625 --> 03:49.042
She treats the company as her family.

03:49.167 --> 03:50.875
The company treats her as animal.

03:52.542 --> 03:54.208
To be honest,

03:54.333 --> 03:55.417
I feel bad for people like her.

03:55.542 --> 03:58.250
I hope I won't be like her when I get old.

03:58.375 --> 04:01.333
Who wants to be like her! Miserable.

04:04.875 --> 04:06.292
<i>I think...</i>

04:06.417 --> 04:08.208
<i>if I ran into this woman</i>

04:08.333 --> 04:10.750
<i>when I was 18,</i>

04:11.208 --> 04:13.333
<i>I would have definitely laughed at her</i>

04:13.458 --> 04:15.417
<i>like them, without mercy.</i>

04:17.708 --> 04:19.666
<i>Yabiyabi. Good evening everyone.</i>

04:19.791 --> 04:21.166
<i>This is Guangyu.</i>

04:21.500 --> 04:24.292
<i>Do you like who you are now?</i>

04:25.292 --> 04:27.167
<i>When we grow up,</i>

04:27.292 --> 04:30.208
<i>we become sophiscated
and tend to compromise</i>

04:30.333 --> 04:31.583
<i>in order to survive.</i>

04:31.708 --> 04:34.792
<i>We become someone we don't recognize.</i>

04:36.375 --> 04:39.167
<i>Would you sometimes
miss the time when you</i>

04:39.292 --> 04:40.917
<i>were rather naive and dared to dream?</i>

04:42.625 --> 04:45.792
<i>Is that part of you still there?</i>

04:46.792 --> 04:49.458
<i>Do you still remember those people</i>

04:49.583 --> 04:50.708
<i>who played an important role in your life?</i>

04:50.833 --> 04:51.875
<i>(My dream: Go to Andy Lau's concert...)</i>

04:53.417 --> 04:54.583
<i>Tonight,</i>

04:54.708 --> 04:56.458
<i>we'll start our program with</i>

04:56.583 --> 04:58.583
<i>this song from me to you all.</i>

04:58.708 --> 05:00.583
<i>A song we haven't heard for a long time.</i>

05:00.708 --> 05:03.542
<i>"Forget Love Water" by Andy Lau.</i>

05:34.708 --> 05:36.667
<i>Good morning. Here is the latest news...</i>

05:36.958 --> 05:38.833
<i>yesterday Alec Su of The Little Tigers</i>

05:38.958 --> 05:42.833
<i>said he dropped out of Taiwan University.</i>

05:42.958 --> 05:45.292
<i>The whole entertainment world is in shock.</i>

06:08.250 --> 06:10.167
Are you giving birth? Are you done or not?

06:10.292 --> 06:11.542
I'm done!

06:15.250 --> 06:17.417
<i>Back then, I was turning 18</i>

06:17.542 --> 06:19.917
<i>and truly understood something important:</i>

06:20.458 --> 06:21.833
<i>History has proven that, there are mainly</i>

06:21.958 --> 06:23.750
<i>two types of young girls in the world.</i>

06:23.875 --> 06:25.542
Hey, here she comes.

06:25.667 --> 06:27.542
Wow! How elegant.

06:27.667 --> 06:29.500
Oh my God! She's gorgeous!

06:29.625 --> 06:31.292
So cute!

06:32.375 --> 06:34.583
<i>Pretty girls who are popular...</i>

06:37.208 --> 06:38.167
D0n't g0!

06:38.417 --> 06:39.375
Wait for me! -Tao Minmin!

06:39.500 --> 06:40.125
<i>And</i>

06:40.250 --> 06:41.792
<i>those who are not pretty.</i>

06:44.292 --> 06:45.542
<i>My name is Lin Truly.</i>

06:46.667 --> 06:47.750
<i>Sorry!</i>

06:48.167 --> 06:49.875
<i>I'm the one who just fell on the street.</i>

06:51.792 --> 06:53.375
<i>If you're a guy,</i>

06:53.792 --> 06:55.667
<i>let me tell you a story of an ordinary girl</i>

06:55.792 --> 06:59.667
<i>who you've never bothered to care about</i>

06:59.792 --> 07:01.917
<i>and her ordinary life.</i>

07:25.708 --> 07:27.167
<i>Back then, the most important decision</i>

07:27.292 --> 07:29.333
<i>we had to make every day</i>

07:29.458 --> 07:32.125
<i>was what to eat for breakfast.</i>

07:32.250 --> 07:33.292
Can you please hurry up?

07:33.417 --> 07:34.792
Is it that tough to decide?

07:37.208 --> 07:39.250
<i>The biggest lie we had ever told</i>

07:39.375 --> 07:40.833
<i>was on the day of exam,</i>

07:40.958 --> 07:42.167
<i>we'd say...</i>

07:42.375 --> 07:43.750
I didn't prepare for it.

07:44.750 --> 07:46.458
Neither did I.

07:46.583 --> 07:48.333
I thought we were having math exam.

07:48.458 --> 07:49.708
<i>The most luxurious thing to do,</i>

07:49.833 --> 07:51.667
<i>was to go shopping in the bookstore.</i>

07:51.792 --> 07:52.792
<i>Back then,</i>

07:52.917 --> 07:55.875
<i>that was our department store.</i>

07:56.583 --> 07:58.208
<i>The biggest dream we had</i>

07:58.333 --> 07:58.833
<i>was to meet our idols</i>

07:58.958 --> 08:00.292
<i>one day.</i>

08:00.417 --> 08:03.583
The shame of being shameless
is shameless

08:05.625 --> 08:07.208
<i>Somehow young girls of that time</i>

08:07.333 --> 08:09.875
<i>had some kind of fantasy.</i>

08:10.583 --> 08:12.292
<i>We believed whoever collected most photos</i>

08:12.417 --> 08:13.042
<i>would be the most qualified person</i>

08:13.167 --> 08:15.167
<i>to marry him.</i>

08:17.542 --> 08:18.667
<i>This is Small.</i>

08:18.792 --> 08:20.417
<i>Although large in size,</i>

08:20.542 --> 08:22.500
<i>she is a super romantic teenage girl.</i>

08:22.792 --> 08:24.417
<i>Kaneshiro Takeshi is her ex,</i>

08:24.542 --> 08:25.250
<i>and now</i>

08:25.375 --> 08:27.625
<i>Aaron Kwok is her fiance.</i>

08:31.792 --> 08:33.417
Even I am not married yet,

08:34.167 --> 08:35.375
how come you already have a husband?

08:36.375 --> 08:37.582
Boss Lau...

08:38.207 --> 08:40.792
However hard you try, he'll never reply.

08:42.292 --> 08:45.167
What you do is called shameless.

08:50.583 --> 08:51.792
<i>This is Meimei.</i>

08:51.917 --> 08:53.417
<i>Very cheerful,</i>

08:53.542 --> 08:56.500
<i>but...almost too cheerful.</i>

08:57.917 --> 09:00.208
Girls, where are you going?

09:01.792 --> 09:04.750
<i>Back in our teenage life, we were always</i>

09:04.875 --> 09:07.583
<i>doing silly things apart from studying.</i>

09:08.375 --> 09:09.500
<i>And this is the silliest</i>

09:09.625 --> 09:11.333
<i>among all.</i>

09:12.667 --> 09:14.708
Ouyang is coming. He's so handsome.

09:14.833 --> 09:16.667
Hey, be quiet. Come on.

09:16.875 --> 09:19.000
He has a style. He's here.

09:22.750 --> 09:24.667
<i>There is always a boy like this,</i>

09:24.792 --> 09:26.542
<i>in every teenage girl's life.</i>

09:30.667 --> 09:31.625
Thank you.

09:36.708 --> 09:37.708
It's on me.

09:38.417 --> 09:39.292
6O please. -60.

09:39.417 --> 09:40.375
6O please. -60.

09:43.250 --> 09:46.417
<i>Somehow they're always basketball players,</i>

09:51.167 --> 09:55.208
<i>secret crush for every girl in the school.</i>

09:58.667 --> 10:01.083
I feel Ouyang is looking at me.

10:01.208 --> 10:03.667
I think he's looking at me.

10:07.333 --> 10:10.667
<i>We can giggle for the whole day</i>

10:10.792 --> 10:12.375
<i>just because of a look from him.</i>

10:19.667 --> 10:21.708
Dear all, can you please stop helping

10:21.833 --> 10:24.250
those idiots send love letters

10:24.375 --> 10:26.250
to our Minmin?

10:26.375 --> 10:27.792
Especially this kind of idiot,

10:27.917 --> 10:30.208
who misused "disney" for "destiny".

10:31.875 --> 10:34.250
<i>This kind of orginary, simple life</i>

10:34.375 --> 10:37.250
<i>was turned upside down by that very letter.</i>

10:41.292 --> 10:42.958
<i>(to Lin Truly)</i>

10:51.167 --> 10:53.042
<i>This is a chain letter from South African</i>

10:53.167 --> 10:54.833
<i>missionary Antnony DE Croud.</i>

10:54.958 --> 10:57.292
<i>Now the good luck is bestowed on you.</i>

10:57.417 --> 10:59.042
<i>Send 5 copies to your friends,</i>

10:59.167 --> 11:00.167
<i>and the good luck is yours.</i>

11:00.292 --> 11:02.917
<i>Otherwise disasters will be waiting for you.</i>

11:03.500 --> 11:04.375
<i>In 1979, Mr. Chen from Taiwan did not</i>

11:04.500 --> 11:07.167
<i>take the letter seriously and tore it apart.</i>

11:07.292 --> 11:09.250
<i>...he died in a car accident the next day.</i>

11:09.375 --> 11:12.458
<i>In 1963, Flayre from Holland burnt it...</i>

11:12.583 --> 11:14.583
<i>3 days later, his mother started to...</i>

11:14.708 --> 11:16.208
<i>suffer an incurable disease.</i>

11:26.167 --> 11:27.667
<i>(You still have three days. Good luck.)</i>

11:34.708 --> 11:37.042
<i>The person I want to send chain letter to</i>

11:37.167 --> 11:38.458
<i>the most, is Lin Sincere.</i>

11:38.792 --> 11:40.042
<i>My brother.</i>

11:40.167 --> 11:41.708
Your brother advanced

11:41.833 --> 11:44.958
5 places in this exam.

11:45.375 --> 11:47.583
Last time he got the lowest score. Besides,

11:47.708 --> 11:49.625
he's spent 7 years on a 5-year program...

11:49.750 --> 11:51.083
Don't you talk back!

11:51.208 --> 11:53.167
Only if you could get half of the grade

11:53.292 --> 11:54.375
of Tao Minmin's.

11:54.625 --> 11:55.958
30 points.

11:56.875 --> 11:57.708
You even tried to alter it

11:57.833 --> 11:58.958
with a different color.

11:59.958 --> 12:01.292
How stupid!

12:01.417 --> 12:03.333
My red pen ran out of ink.

12:03.458 --> 12:05.250
Couldn't you borrow one from your teacher?

12:05.375 --> 12:05.958
That's right.

12:07.792 --> 12:08.792
Take it.

12:09.375 --> 12:10.667
Thank you mom.

12:10.792 --> 12:11.500
Take one more.

12:11.625 --> 12:12.625
Thank you dad!

12:15.750 --> 12:18.333
<i>Many of you probably
had the same thought,</i>

12:18.792 --> 12:22.458
<i>"Am I'm really my parents' child?"</i>

12:22.583 --> 12:25.167
<i>But if my brother's family is really ruined,</i>

12:25.292 --> 12:26.917
<i>I might suffer as well.</i>

12:27.542 --> 12:29.208
<i>So I dismissed that idea.</i>

12:30.625 --> 12:31.625
<i>Therefore...</i>

12:32.208 --> 12:33.458
<i>I gave the first letter</i>

12:33.583 --> 12:34.958
<i>to him.</i>

12:36.500 --> 12:37.583
Lin Truly.

12:38.417 --> 12:39.583
Question 1:

12:40.375 --> 12:43.167
If the balls are put in the order of red,

12:43.292 --> 12:45.625
blue, green, what's the color of ball 555?

12:46.792 --> 12:48.333
It's ok if you don't know the answer,

12:49.625 --> 12:52.375
but why drawing it like this?

12:53.208 --> 12:53.667
Don't you dodge!

12:53.792 --> 12:55.208
<i>There must be a psycho teacher like this</i>

12:55.333 --> 12:57.375
<i>in everyone's school years.</i>

12:57.792 --> 12:59.500
<i>"Wang Baidan"</i>

12:59.875 --> 13:02.167
<i>Our home room teacher and math teacher.</i>

13:02.375 --> 13:03.708
<i>We all call him</i>

13:03.833 --> 13:05.458
<i>"Wang Badan" (asshole)</i>

13:07.167 --> 13:08.375
I haven't even started!

13:08.500 --> 13:09.500
Come back.

13:10.500 --> 13:11.750
You're even louder than me.

13:33.167 --> 13:34.458
<i>I gave the second letter</i>

13:34.583 --> 13:35.875
<i>to Tao Minmin.</i>

13:36.625 --> 13:38.458
<i>It's definitely not because I envy her</i>

13:38.583 --> 13:40.208
<i>for her beauty or popularity.</i>

13:40.333 --> 13:41.333
<i>Not even because</i>

13:41.458 --> 13:43.208
<i>she's that girl who could</i>

13:43.333 --> 13:44.708
<i>get his attention.</i>

13:47.917 --> 13:52.208
<i>It's simply because she lives next door.</i>

13:52.583 --> 13:54.292
<i>Right on my way home.</i>

14:08.542 --> 14:10.042
What? A good student?

14:10.208 --> 14:11.750
Do the recycling.

14:17.583 --> 14:18.667
Hey you.

14:19.583 --> 14:20.708
Kick it back.

14:31.958 --> 14:33.708
Ouyang Extraordinary.

14:35.292 --> 14:37.542
I might've seen this disgusting name before.

14:37.667 --> 14:40.042
<i>As there is a "God" in every school,</i>

14:40.167 --> 14:42.875
<i>there is also a "boss".</i>

14:47.375 --> 14:48.375
Stand up.

14:54.667 --> 14:56.417
<i>Hsu Taiyu.</i>

14:56.708 --> 14:59.208
<i>Last number of the last class in 3rd grade.</i>

14:59.500 --> 15:02.250
<i>He's the boss who leads our school in</i>

15:02.375 --> 15:03.833
<i>turf wars and charge others protection fee.</i>

15:04.375 --> 15:04.708
<i>Rumor has it that</i>

15:04.833 --> 15:08.292
<i>he fights, runs away from home,
he's on drug</i>

15:08.417 --> 15:09.792
<i>has killed people, set fire...</i>

15:09.917 --> 15:12.542
<i>So notorious that no school wants him,</i>

15:12.667 --> 15:14.417
<i>except for First High School...</i>

15:14.750 --> 15:16.042
How daring are you to be here.

15:16.167 --> 15:17.500
You despise us
the 12 Masters of First High?

15:18.792 --> 15:21.250
What about Ten Brothers
from Chuoshui River?

15:21.875 --> 15:23.167
Kill them.

15:33.333 --> 15:35.833
<i>He's even appointed as school patrol</i>

15:35.958 --> 15:37.042
Indecent clothing.

15:37.167 --> 15:38.125
Eating while walking.

15:38.250 --> 15:39.417
Studying too hard.

15:41.667 --> 15:42.500
Too matured body.

15:44.375 --> 15:45.292
<i>First High...</i>

15:45.417 --> 15:47.792
<i>has since been trapped
in the devil's clutches.</i>

15:49.167 --> 15:50.375
Recycle it!

16:00.750 --> 16:01.875
Hey, what are you doing?

16:02.167 --> 16:03.875
Why bully others like this?

16:04.833 --> 16:05.917
What the hell are you guys doing?

16:06.917 --> 16:08.333
Here comes the director,

16:08.917 --> 16:10.542
let's go.

16:14.750 --> 16:17.083
Come on! Go, go.

16:20.875 --> 16:21.958
Chicken.

16:29.167 --> 16:30.542
<i>Therefore...</i>

16:30.875 --> 16:32.625
<i>I decided to send him the third letter.</i>

16:50.792 --> 16:51.500
Guile.

16:51.625 --> 16:53.375
G your mother.

16:59.875 --> 17:00.958
Sorry

17:07.708 --> 17:09.166
<i>(to Hsu Taiyu)</i>

17:12.166 --> 17:13.375
it's pink

17:13.750 --> 17:15.208
with fragrance.

17:15.333 --> 17:17.416
Love letter?

17:17.541 --> 17:18.333
Aren't you over the moon, boss?

17:18.458 --> 17:20.416
Over what! Get lost.

17:24.375 --> 17:26.333
Who has the guts to write him a love letter?

17:26.458 --> 17:27.833
Oh, he was even blushing.

17:27.958 --> 17:29.792
Blushing! Hahahaha

17:29.917 --> 17:31.667
He must be over the moon now.

17:32.250 --> 17:33.583
Not just over the moon...

17:33.708 --> 17:37.292
Over the whole world!

17:39.167 --> 17:43.500
Boss.

17:44.458 --> 17:46.125
Did you hear about it already?

17:46.250 --> 17:48.625
Hsu Taiyu had a car accident yesterday.

17:58.250 --> 18:00.417
Lin Truly...

18:08.375 --> 18:10.667
If I find out who cursed boss,

18:10.917 --> 18:13.583
<i>I'll</i> make sure to break his arms and legs.

18:13.708 --> 18:15.792
Sorry, she needs to take her medicine.

18:16.625 --> 18:18.458
Lin Truly, let's go.

18:18.583 --> 18:20.375
Why are you so heavy!

18:25.917 --> 18:26.583
Go.

18:27.375 --> 18:28.083
Boss, watch your step.

18:28.208 --> 18:30.083
Someone is spreading the rumor,

18:30.208 --> 18:31.750
saying this year's school anniversary

18:32.250 --> 18:35.167
will be suspended due to track renovation.

18:35.583 --> 18:37.167
Let me clarify it here.

18:37.875 --> 18:39.500
This year, school anniversary festival

18:40.375 --> 18:42.333
will be held as scheduled.

18:45.208 --> 18:48.542
