01:56:38.583 --> 01:56:39.875
like you a lot.

01:57:02.375 --> 01:57:03.583
Lin Truly.

01:57:06.583 --> 01:57:08.750
If you already listened to the whole tape,

01:57:11.542 --> 01:57:14.417
just look up at the sky.

01:57:16.708 --> 01:57:18.875
Then I will know

01:57:20.375 --> 01:57:22.625
I'm looking at the same starry sky

01:57:24.542 --> 01:57:26.375
as the girl I like.

01:57:29.792 --> 01:57:32.167
I Love You

01:58:33.792 --> 01:58:37.167
<i>(The person I like: Hsu Taiyu)</i>

01:58:48.417 --> 01:58:50.042
<i>You were always wondering...</i>

01:58:50.167 --> 01:58:52.375
<i>what your future would be like.</i>

01:58:52.833 --> 01:58:54.750
<i>Now...l can give you the answer.</i>

01:58:59.208 --> 01:59:00.542
Give me the salary

01:59:00.667 --> 01:59:02.042
