01:59:19.292 --> 01:59:20.917
Truly! Truly!

01:59:21.375 --> 01:59:22.583
What the fuck!

01:59:22.708 --> 01:59:25.417
Handwritten resignation letter...so ancient.

01:59:25.542 --> 01:59:26.792
