01:59:57.542 --> 01:59:59.458
It's true I gave you the bill quite late.

01:59:59.583 --> 02:00:00.042
But it doesn't mean you could...

02:00:00.167 --> 02:00:00.750
<i>In the future...</i>

02:00:00.875 --> 02:00:02.625
<i>you won't really become someone amazing.</i>

02:00:02.958 --> 02:00:04.625
<i>You still make mistakes.</i>

02:00:04.750 --> 02:00:06.167
<i>You still get confused.</i>

02:00:06.792 --> 02:00:09.083
<i>You still regret for not having more ice,</i>

02:00:09.208 --> 02:00:10.458
<i>or not experiencing more relationships.</i>

02:00:10.583 --> 02:00:11.792
...that's what I don't like about you.

02:00:11.917 --> 02:00:13.750
Same here.

02:00:18.917 --> 02:00:20.417
Let's break up.

02:00:21.667 --> 02:00:23.875
<i>...and being too kind to people you dislike.</i>

02:00:24.292 --> 02:00:26.375
<i>And cherishing people you like more.</i>

02:00:26.792 --> 02:00:28.042
<i>But...</i>

02:00:28.167 --> 02:00:29.750
<i>the way you are is good.</i>

02:00:30.583 --> 02:00:31.583
<i>You're still very brave,</i>

02:00:31.708 --> 02:00:33.250
<i>very naive.</i>

02:00:33.375 --> 02:00:34.458
<i>You still...</i>

02:00:34.583 --> 02:00:36.083
